      "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese </strong>finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Crush your <strong>crispy onions</strong> in their bag</p><p>Combine most of the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> (save a little for garnish!) and <strong>crushed crispy onions</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>crispy onion crumb</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-4-1688642915834-x200.jpg",
