            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> with your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 8-9 min or until the sliced peppers are tender and the sauce has thickened – these are your <strong>smoky peppers</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-2-1688642929227-x200.jpg",
