            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-2-1688642933348-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>corn</strong> from the <strong>cooked cobettes </strong>(careful they will be hot!), then sprinkle the <strong>crispy onion crumb</strong> over the top (for a little extra indulgence add a knob of butter!)</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave the cobettes whole and don't add the crispy onion crumb!</span></strong></p><p>Divide the <strong>smoky peppers </strong>evenly between the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong> and top with the <strong>grated cheese</strong> and <strong>reserved chopped coriander</strong>, then season to taste and enjoy!</p>",
